<%- include('partials/head',{title:'About',isPublic:true,canonicalPath:'/about',description:'Scheduling without the group-chat scramble. Musalla helps Musallas and Masajid coordinate imam, salah, and khutbah schedules in one thoughtful place.',structuredData:{'@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'AboutPage',name:'About Musalla',url:`${baseUrl}/about`,description:'A thoughtful scheduling home for imam, salah, and khutbah coordination in Musallas and Masajid.'}}) %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/about-carousel.css?v=1">
<main class="about-page">
  <%- include('partials/public-nav') %>
  <header class="about-hero"><p class="eyebrow">ABOUT MUSALLA</p><h1>Scheduling without the group-chat scramble.</h1><p>Musalla gives prayer communities one thoughtful place to coordinate imam and khutbah schedules. It brings the clarity of a modern staff scheduler to Musallas and Masajid—without losing sight of the people and purpose behind every salah.</p></header>
  <section class="about-grid"><article class="surface"><span aria-hidden="true">☾</span><h2>One clear schedule</h2><p>Keep imam assignments, salah coverage, and khutbah schedules organized without searching through scattered messages or spreadsheets.</p></article><article class="surface"><span aria-hidden="true">⌂</span><h2>One community home</h2><p>A dedicated workspace for imams and Musalla administrators to coordinate their prayer community—not a general community directory or social app.</p></article><article class="surface"><span aria-hidden="true">♡</span><h2>More time to serve</h2><p>Imams can volunteer where help is needed, administrators can see what is covered, and everyone spends less time coordinating.</p></article></section>
  <section class="app-showcase" aria-labelledby="app-showcase-title">
    <div class="app-showcase-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">INSIDE THE APP</p><h2 id="app-showcase-title">See Musalla in action</h2></div><div class="carousel-buttons"><button id="app-carousel-previous" type="button" aria-label="Previous screenshot">‹</button><button id="app-carousel-next" type="button" aria-label="Next screenshot">›</button></div></div>
